that I can't believe

1025
00:40:13,513 --> 00:40:15,481
you did all of this
in one day.

1026
00:40:15,565 --> 00:40:17,566
Well, I've been working on it
since I got home.

1027
00:40:17,633 --> 00:40:19,735
