1040
00:40:57,474 --> 00:40:58,807
Scottie.

1041
00:41:00,727 --> 00:41:02,444
What's wrong?

1042
00:41:02,512 --> 00:41:03,612
You were in such
a good mood earlier.

1043
00:41:03,679 --> 00:41:04,846
What happened?

1044
00:41:04,898 --> 00:41:08,317
- I was.
