1046
00:41:17,160 --> 00:41:18,460
What?

1047
00:41:18,528 --> 00:41:19,995
He figured out that
you set the whole thing up,

1048
00:41:20,046 --> 00:41:22,331
and he came to me.
So what?

1049
00:41:22,382 --> 00:41:24,083
What does that have to do
with anything?

1050
00:41:24,167 --> 00:41:27,202
You can survive this.
