1057
00:41:39,149 --> 00:41:40,882
Yes.

1058
00:41:45,355 --> 00:41:48,407
Okay.
Tell me what it is.

1059
00:41:48,491 --> 00:41:50,409
I can't.

1060
00:41:52,829 --> 00:41:53,746
Guess we're not
sharing everything

1061
00:41:53,830 --> 00:41:54,896
